column1: Allow user to select a store for booking
column26:
Steps:

1.Enter the URL: [Wall Painting Design Ideas & Room Paint Designs for Home Painting - Asian Paints|https://www.asianpaints.com/inspiration/ideas/inspiration-gallery.html]

2.Scroll down the page to find a Find a store option

3.Allow user to enter the 6 digit pin correctly

4.Then click on Go

5. User get the results of near by Asian paints store by Store locator 

6.User can select the store for booking successfully

column1: Allow User to click Enquire now in Ideas gallery  in ideas
column26:
Steps:

1.Enter the URL: [Wall Painting Design Ideas & Room Paint Designs for Home Painting - Asian Paints|https://www.asianpaints.com/inspiration/ideas/inspiration-gallery.html]

2. Click on enquire now 

3.Allow user to enter Username \[A-Z characters], email, mobile number\[10 digits] and pin\[6 digit] code successfully  

4.Then click on Enquire now 

5. User get the free site evaluation by an Asian paints safe painting service expert successfully.

column1: Allow user to click on paint budget calculator
column26:
# User should enter the following website [https://www.asianpaints.com/|https://www.asianpaints.com/|smart-link] 
# After that click on Paints and textures tab
# Once clicking on paints and textures tab user will able to see paint budget calculator heading
# User should click on paint budget calculator heading which will show new page.
# In new page user has to select type of painting whether it is fresh painting or re-painting
# After this user has to select whether painting is for exterior or interior and also the size of the home
# After selecting size of the home  user should select carpet area
# After selecting all this option their is calculate now button user need to click on that button which will calculate the entire paint budget
